HEADWORD: Alkalization
<hw>Al`ka*li*za"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>alcalisation</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of rendering alkaline by
impregnating with an alkali; a conferring of alkaline
qualities.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

